# Rectangle point/area searches: closest, overlapping, enclosed.
canvas -width 400 -height 300
do create rectangle 10 10 100 100
do create rectangle 50 50 150 150 -fill red
q find closest 55 55
q find closest 30 30
q find closest 200 200
q find overlapping 0 0 20 20
q find overlapping 120 120 140 140
q find overlapping 45 45 55 55
q find overlapping 20 20 40 40
q find enclosed 0 0 160 160
q find enclosed 5 5 105 105
q find enclosed 40 40 160 160
q find closest 55 55 0 2
q find closest 55 55 0 1
